    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-061__align-001">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-061</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 61.1 - 老子 61.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 61.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>大國者下流，天下之交。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>What makes a great state is its being (like) a low-lying, down- flowing (stream);</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-061__align-002">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-061</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 61.3 - 老子 61.4</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 61.2 - 老子 61.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>天下之牝，牝常以靜勝牡，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>- it becomes the centre to which tend (all the small states) under heaven. (To illustrate from) the case of all females:</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-061__align-003">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-061</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 61.5</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 61.4</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>以靜為下。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>- the female always overcomes the male by her stillness.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-061__align-004">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-061</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 61.6</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 61.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>則取小國；</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Stillness may be considered (a sort of) abasement.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-061__align-005">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-061</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 61.7 - 老子 61.8</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 61.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>小國以下大國，則取大國。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Thus it is that a great state, by condescending to small states, gains them for itself;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-061__align-006">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-061</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">2</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 61.9 - 老子 61.10</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 61.7</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>故或下以取，或下而取。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>and that small states, by abasing themselves to a great state, win it over to them.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-061__align-007">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-061</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 61.11</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 61.8</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>大國不過欲兼畜人，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>In the one case the abasement leads to gaining adherents, in the other case to procuring favour.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-061__align-008">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-061</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 61.12</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 61.9</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>小國不過欲入事人。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The great state only wishes to unite men together and nourish them;</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-061__align-009">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-061</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 61.13</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 61.10</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>夫兩者各得其所欲，</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>a small state only wishes to be received by, and to serve, the other.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="laozi-chapter-061__align-010">
      <prop type="x-work-id">laozi</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-id">laozi-chapter-061</prop>
      <prop type="x-section-unit">chapter</prop>
      <prop type="x-segment-type">sentence</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-granularity">grouped</prop>
      <prop type="x-is-coarse-alignment">false</prop>
      <prop type="x-alignment-type">exact_or_near_exact</prop>
      <prop type="x-confidence">1.00</prop>
      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">老子 61.14</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">老子 61.11</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>大者宜為下。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Each gets what it desires, but the great state must learn to abase itself.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
  </body>
